    "en": {
      "title": "Laugh Gas price down by 1050",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. W. K. H. Vagapitiya, chairman of Laugh Gas Company, says that the price of a domestic gas cylinder will be reduced by 1050 rupees from midnight tonight.",
        "Accordingly, the price of 12.50 kg cylinder will decrease by 1050 and simultaneously the price of 5 kg cylinder will also decrease.",
        "Accordingly, the new price of 12.50 kg will be 5800 rupees. Laugh Gas Company says that the price of a 5 kg cylinder has been reduced to 2320 and the price of a kg to 928"
      ],
